{UTF-8}
Base Time=20
	~	Minute
	~		|

Car Commuters= INTEG (Car Commuters + Switch to Cars-Switch to Transit,
		5000)
	~	Person
	~		|

Car Travel Time=Base Time * (1 + (Car Commuters / Road Capacity)^4)
	~	Minute
	~		|

Public Transit Users= INTEG (Switch to Transit-Switch to Cars,
		1000)
	~	Person
	~		|

Road Capacity=6000
	~	Car
	~		|

Road Congestion=Car Commuters / Road Capacity
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Switch to Cars=Public Transit Users * (Transit Travel Time / Car Travel Time) * 0.02
	~	Person/Month
	~		|

Switch to Transit=Car Commuters * (Car Travel Time / 30) * 0.01
	~	Person/Month
	~		|

Transit Quality=Public Transit Users * 0.05
	~	Dmnl
	~		|

Transit Travel Time=40 / (Transit Quality + 1)
	~	Minute
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 120
	~	Month
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Month
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP 
	~	Month [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 0.25
	~	Month [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

